title: Question about "Little Devil Teemo Icon"!
body: I can see on a web page it says "*Icons will be granted up to two weeks after November 3, 2016 at 23:59 PT." And on the Little Devil Teemo Icone it says "Unlocked for your account by defeating Dooms Bot of Doom by 11/3/2016 at 23:59 PT" I have played Dooms Bot of Doom and won the 1/3 and 4/3. Will that mean I'm not able to get this delicious icon {{item:3070}} {{item:3070}}

replies.body: I haven't gotten mine yet, either. And I own the skin.
Just got mine, only played one game and didn't even realize they were giving it out. Googled it and it came up to this. Thought i'd let you guys know they are coming.

It means that Icons are being granted until Nov 17th, so sit tight until yours arrives. If you don't have it by the time the 18th rolls around, [hit us up](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) and we'll assist you further.
